HEADWORD: Sea pie
<hw>Sea" pie</hw> <pr>(s⟦emac⟧" p⟦imac⟧`)</pr>. <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>The oyster catcher, a limicoline bird of the genus
<gen>Haematopus</gen>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

