==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Sea pie
<hw>Sea" pie`</hw>. <def>A dish of crust or pastry and meat or fish,
etc., cooked together in alternate layers, -- a common food of sailors;
<as>as, a three-decker <ex>sea pie</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Seapiece</ent>⟦br⟧
